snippet.title: Control : Override Teaser Trailer (Wishlist now on steam)
snippet.description:
Control : Override is an upcoming puzzle game for pc. 
Wishlist On Steam :https://store.steampowered.com/app/1406090/ControlOverride/

Developed by B-Deshi Interactive.
Originally made for the GMTK 2020 Game Jam. 
This is a re-imagined version with better graphics, story and way more levels.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/B_DeshiDev
